title: WUJIE
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Asian, Fusion
description: 大蔬无界, at 南京德基广场馆, is part of an upscale vegetarian restaurant group. English spoken and has English menu with photos & icons which labels items if containing egg, dairy, or onion. Extensive lineup of macarons & Swiss rolls. Free WIFI available. Chinese credit card okay.
streetAddress: Deji Plaza Second Phase 6F, Zhongshan Rd18, Xuan Wu District
